flowchart TB
    subgraph EYES["👁 Eyes 眼睛模块 — 盯市场"]
        direction TB
        RSS[fetch_rss.py<br>RSS 多源抓取]
        PRICE[fetch_price_router.py<br>三源价格路由]
        API[fetch_market_api.py<br>市场事件 API]
        NEWS[fetch_finnhub_news.py<br>个股新闻]

        INSIGHT[SOP_市场洞察<br>P13 分析 → 每日市场日报]
        RADAR[SOP_投资雷达<br>趋势 + 价格 + 信号 → 桥接报告]

        RSS --> INSIGHT
        API --> INSIGHT
        NEWS --> INSIGHT
        PRICE --> RADAR
        INSIGHT -->|下一步建议| RADAR
    end

    subgraph BRAIN["🧠 Brain 大脑模块 — 做分析"]
        direction TB
        PCHAIN[P1-P16 提示词资产<br>Brain/references/]
        STRATEGY[SOP_策略分析<br>5 条策略路由]
        RESEARCH[SOP_初始调研<br>P1→P4→P2→P9]
        DIAGNOSIS[投资诊断模块<br>ymos-diagnosis/]

        PCHAIN --> STRATEGY
        PCHAIN --> RESEARCH
    end

    subgraph STATE["🏷️ 持仓与关注 — 管状态"]
        direction TB
        PREF_DOC[当前关注方向与投资偏好.md<br>系统灵魂文件]
        HOLD_SM[持仓_状态机.md<br>持仓真相源]
        WATCH_SM[Watchlist_状态机.md<br>关注真相源]
        STOCK_DIR[个股文件夹<br>知识库 + 研报 + 备忘录]
        VIEW[持仓备忘录_视图.md<br>1 分钟扫盘看板]
        DASH[Dashboard HTML<br>可视化看板]
        CLOSE_SOP[SOP_持仓收口<br>一致性校验 + 刷新视图]
    end

    RADAR -->|暗号路由建议| STRATEGY
    STRATEGY -->|写回分析结果| STOCK_DIR
    RESEARCH -->|建档| STOCK_DIR
    STRATEGY -->|更新状态| HOLD_SM
    STRATEGY -->|更新状态| WATCH_SM
    CLOSE_SOP --> VIEW
    CLOSE_SOP --> DASH
    PREF_DOC -.->|驱动策略分析| STRATEGY
    PREF_DOC -.->|驱动雷达过滤| RADAR

    EYES ~~~ BRAIN
    BRAIN ~~~ STATE

